                <tr><th>Live vaccine was administered in the last 4 weeks</th><th>boolean</th><th>0</th><th>1</th><th>Out</th></tr>
              
                <tr><th>MCV1 was administered</th><th>boolean</th><th>0</th><th>1</th><th>Out</th></tr>
              
